"{\n  \"text\": \"So I'm getting asked why am I doing these stupid videos about my garden and composting and all this other stuff? And it's because I'm going to be trying to sell the cucumbers that I have growing in these six rows at the farmer's market. I'm going to grow the cucumbers, I'm going to ferment the cucumbers, value adding, and then I'm going to sell them for an upsell price higher than I would normal produce because this is special produce. This is produce that I grew with my own hands, but more than that, that is completely biologically able, completely biologically there. It comes from compost. This is as biologically rich as I can make it. And so that's what I'm looking to do with these videos is to talk about that to upsell my pickles and okra that I make later this season, and that I'm going to be selling at the farmer's market for a little bit more than you pay for your normal produce. Thanks, y'all.\",\n  \"sentences\": [\n    {\n      \"text\": \" So I'm getting asked why am I doing these stupid videos about my garden and composting and all this other stuff?\",\n      \"start\": 0.16,\n      \"end\": 5.2,\n      \"duration\": 5.04,\n      \"confidence\": 0.994,\n      \"tokens\": [\n        {\n          \"text\": \" So\",\n          \"start\": 0.16,\n          \"end\": 0.24,\n          \"duration\": 0.08,\n          \"confidence\": 0.998\n        },\n        {\n          \"text\": \" I\",\n          \"start\": 0.32,\n          \"end\": 0.4,\n          \"duration\": 0.08,\n          \"confidence\": 0.999\n        },\n        {\n          \"text\": \"'\",\n          \"start\": 0.4,\n          \"end\": 0.48,\n          \"duration\": 0.08,\n          \"confidence\": 1.0\n        },\n        {\n          \"text\": \"m\",\n          \"start\": 0.48,\n          \"end\": 0.56,\n          \"duration\": 0.08,\n          \"confidence\": 1.0\n        },\n        {\n          \"text\": \" g\",\n          \"start\": 0.56,\n          \"end\": 0.64,\n          